/* ==UserStyle==
@name Hyperpipe Catppuccin
@namespace github.com/catppuccin/userstyles/styles/hyperpipe
@homepageURL https://github.com/catppuccin/userstyles/tree/main/styles/hyperpipe
@version 0.1.0
